author: Epictetus
message: First say to yourself what you would be; and then do what you have to do.
title: Thought of the day

author: Carl Jung
message: Through pride we are ever deceiving ourselves. But deep down below the surface of the average conscience a still, small voice says to us, Something is out of tune.
title: Thought of the day

author: Epictetus
message: Keep silence for the most part, and speak only when you must, and then briefly.
title: Thought of the day

author: Percy Shelley
message: Fear not for the future, weep not for the past.
title: Thought of the day
